<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <h1 style="color: #000; margin-bottom: 5px;">363 PHOTOGRAPHY</h1>
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">Refund Processed Successfully</p>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Dear <%= @appointment.name %>,</p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">We're pleased to inform you that your refund for request <strong>#<%= @refund_request.id %></strong> has been processed successfully.</p>

  <div style="background-color: #d1ecf1; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-left: 4px solid #0c5460;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #0c5460;">Refund Processed</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #0c5460;"><strong>Amount:</strong> ₦<%= number_with_delimiter(@refund_request.refund_amount) %></p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #0c5460;">The refund has been processed to your bank account. Depending on your bank, it may take 1-3 business days for the funds to appear in your account.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Transaction Details</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Request Date:</strong> <%= @refund_request.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Processed Date:</strong> <%= @refund_request.processed_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Bank Account:</strong> <%= @refund_request.account_name %> - <%= @refund_request.bank_name %></p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Account Number:</strong> <%= @refund_request.account_number[0..3] %>******</p>
    <% if @refund_request.admin_notes.present? %>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Processing Notes:</strong> <%= @refund_request.admin_notes.lines.last %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px;">Thank you for your patience throughout this process. If you have any questions or if the refund does not appear in your account within 3 business days, please contact our customer service team by replying to this email or calling us at <%= Appointment::STUDIO_NUMBERS[@appointment.location.downcase] || '08144985074' %>.</p>

  <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px;">Thank you for your business,</p>
  <p style="margin-top: 0;">363 Photography Team</p>

  <div style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888;">
    <p>This is an automated email from 363 Photography.</p>
    <p>© <%= Date.today.year %> 363 Photography. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</div>
